<!-- 花草百科全书 - 首页（科技感设计） -->
<!-- 风格：渐变背景 + 大圆角卡片 + 层次分明 -->

<view class="container">
  <!-- 渐变背景 -->
  <view class="gradient-bg"></view>
  
  <!-- 主内容区 -->
  <view class="main-content">
    <!-- 品牌 + 植物视觉 -->
    <view class="hero-section">
      <view class="brand">
        <text class="brand-name">花草百科全书</text>
        <text class="brand-slogan">AI 智能识别 · 一拍即知</text>
      </view>
      <image class="plant-visual" src="/images/monstera.png" mode="aspectFit"></image>
    </view>
    
    <!-- 核心功能卡片 -->
    <view class="feature-card">
      <view class="card-header">
        <text class="card-title">智能识别</text>
        <text class="card-subtitle">AI 驱动 · 精准识别</text>
      </view>
      
      <view class="action-buttons">
        <view class="action-btn primary" bindtap="takePhoto">
          <view class="btn-icon-bg">
            <text class="btn-icon">📷</text>
          </view>
          <text class="btn-label">拍照识别</text>
        </view>
        
        <view class="action-btn" bindtap="chooseFromAlbum">
          <view class="btn-icon-bg outline">
            <text class="btn-icon">🖼️</text>
          </view>
          <text class="btn-label">相册上传</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    
    <!-- 快捷功能 -->
    <view class="quick-grid">
      <view class="quick-card" bindtap="goToMyPlants">
        <view class="quick-icon-bg green">
          <text class="quick-icon">🌱</text>
        </view>
        <text class="quick-title">我的花园</text>
        <text class="quick-count" wx:if="{{todayWaterCount > 0}}">{{todayWaterCount}}待浇水</text>
      </view>
      
      <view class="quick-card" bindtap="goToSearch">
        <view class="quick-icon-bg blue">
          <text class="quick-icon">🔍</text>
        </view>
        <text class="quick-title">搜索植物</text>
      </view>
      
      <view class="quick-card" bindtap="goToHistory">
        <view class="quick-icon-bg purple">
          <text class="quick-icon">📋</text>
        </view>
        <text class="quick-title">识别历史</text>
      </view>
      
      <view class="quick-card" bindtap="goToChat">
        <view class="quick-icon-bg orange">
          <text class="quick-icon">🤖</text>
        </view>
        <text class="quick-title">AI 助手</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  
  <!-- 底部提示 -->
  <view class="footer-hint">
    <text class="hint-text">左滑查看更多功能</text>
    <text class="hint-arrow">←</text>
  </view>
</view>